android
-------

layout
------
linear layout ( first android layout)
relative layout	
constrate layout (power full layout)(support by google)


layout_height / width
-------------

-match_parent (fill screen side)
-wrap_content (depend on program content)


Orientation
------------
android:orientation=""
-vertical
-horizontal

Size value 
----------	
sp (font size)
dp (Margin and time

padding = inside 
margin  = outside

Relative layout
---------------

android:layout_below	
android:layout_toRightOf	
android:layout_toLeftOf

Image View
----------
		android:id="@+id/image"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="200dp"
        android:src="@drawable/view"
        android:scaleType="centerCrop"
        android:contentDescription="@string/description"
		
		
		2F6394
		
		
constraite layout
-----------------

must have minimum one horizontal and vertical constraite
if set margin value only work constraiteof 

layout_constraintLeft_toLeftOf

layout_constraintLeft_toRightOf

layout_constraintRight_toLeftOf

layout_constraintRight_toRightOf

layout_constraintTop_toTopOf

layout_constraintTop_toBottomOf

layout_constraintBottom_toTopOf

layout_constraintBottom_toBottomOf

layout_constraintBaseline_toBaselineOf

layout_constraintStart_toEndOf

layout_constraintStart_toStartOf

layout_constraintEnd_toStartOf

layout_constraintEnd_toEndOf




